The players start the round by creating a 1 v 1 tournament bracket.

Each round a player flips a coin:
    if heads => They play Beer Ball
    if tails => They play Beer Pong

Beer Ball is player with 1 full solo cup of Beer.

Beer Pong is played with 6 cups. Players may arrange the cups however they want.

1 point is awarded for a round won!

Winnier of the tournanment gets 3 points!

No Violent Energy allowed! 1 drink per offense!